Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:16.93,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}優しく食むわ　あなたの全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:35.48,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}気づく　目を見開いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.96,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}仄青い混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.44,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}冷たく私を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.42,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}そして抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:51.96,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}あなたのいないその体で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.76,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}吐き出しその生命は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:22:02.11,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}まだ形を残しているわ　紅く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:04.73,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}鮮やかな永遠が見えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.81,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}隣でそれは歌いだすわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:15.73,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}ねえ　私を愛して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:20.33,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}離さないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.67,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}All is calm All is bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:09.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}在耳边细语的天使堕入凡间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:16.93,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我会将你温柔地蚕食殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:22.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:35.48,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}回过神 眼瞳空洞地睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.96,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}这暗蓝色的混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.44,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}冰冷地将我包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.42,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}而后将我揽入胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:51.96,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}用你那已经失去灵魂的躯体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.76,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}濒临崩溃的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:22:02.11,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}仍勉强维持姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:04.73,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我能看见那赤红绚丽的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}它就在我身旁放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.93,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}What was I born for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:15.73,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}请深爱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:20.33,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我绝不离开你
